VSo I'll be talking about the success of my campus,
p4
aVthe University of Maryland, Baltimore County, UMBC,
p5
aVin educating students of all types,
p6
aVacross the arts and humanities and the science and engineering areas.
p7
aVWhat makes our story especially important
p8
aVis that we have learned so much from a group of students
p9
aVwho are typically not at the top of the academic ladder \u2014
p10
aVstudents of color, students underrepresented in selected areas.
p11
aVAnd what makes the story especially unique
p12
aVis that we have learned how to help African-American students, Latino students,
p13
aVstudents from low-income backgrounds,
p14
aVto become some of the best in the world in science and engineering.
